aces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪覺得有本事搞散人地家庭突顯自己有市場呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢種人道德觀咁低既人好難明佢諗咩"},{"pid":"e2d2c4a1dab8070ecda535d42af1635644509c91","tid":491094,"uid":31381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T12:36:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9c80a4e4196be224e8ca9fad569856467d7c13a","tid":491094,"uid":57962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T12:50:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ea973ef31a40cedc3f57ef6d5d5f053d88a66779","tid":491094,"uid":131731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T13:06:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4aa27134d7c7e8ceef80ba547d247efb1f83d65","tid":491094,"uid":162028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T16:06:59.000Z","msg":"呢d 人 果價值觀真係好奇怪<br />\n以前一齊過， 自問唔會再追返<br />\n值唔值得， 就問你自己"}]}